{"tid":153282,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[Switch/WiiU][Zelda] 薩爾達傳說:荒野之息 討論區 (3)","createTime":"2017-03-12T12:49:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-09T14:41:29.000Z","uid":36509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"be8e1fd7058509129c64abb0ddcf6bbe9f0b7857","tid":153282,"uid":36509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T12:49:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>劇透討論請用粉色細字</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nQ: 有無得隨時轉英/日文?<br />\nA: 有,入Switch setting轉語言就得<br />\n<br />\nQ: 一開始拎完地圖要做乜?<br />\nA: <span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">解附近嗰四個神社(Shrine)</span></span><br />\n<br />\nQ: 雪山點上?<br />\nA: 手持火把/整+食防寒食物(煮過嘅Spicy Peppers)/著防寒裝<br />\n<br />\nQ: 點拎防寒裝?<br />\nA: 三種方法:<br />\n1)去Great Plateau南面呀伯間屋有個食譜,跟住黎煮俾佢食就得<br />\n2)拎完飛行器去Great Plateau南面呀伯間屋<br />\n3)上雪山頂位揾呀伯<br />\n<br />\nQ: 點煮野食?<br />\nA: 有啲火堆上面有個爐, hold住食材行埋去撳A就有得煮<br />\n<br />\nQ: 解完任去邊揾呀伯?<br />\nA: <span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">四個Shrine交叉點</span></span><br />\n<br />\nQ: 做完XXX唔知點好<br />\nA: 周圍行下實有野做 依隻game係真係open world 無限你一定要做乜唔做乜<br />\n<br />\nTips:<br />\n1)唔慣用X跳可以入setting轉用B跳<br />\n2)解迷卡關時不坊諗下自己有咩能力同埋睇下一入去個牌有咩提示<br />\n3)冰能力除左結冰仲可以解冰 唔夠打咪Skip住先囉<br />\n4)善用地圖個貼紙功能mark低邊度有特別素材/礦之類<br />\n5)拎到相機後見到乜都影下儲圖鑑+可以用sensor搵野<br />\n6)Guardian啲炮可以古代盾ZL+A反射<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/HUlZG.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FHUlZG.md.jpg&h=5935766e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n預告:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1rPxiXXxftE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D1rPxiXXxftE&d=aS0Zid%2FrEVnhaHfkh5i1ak%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=deabf090\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1rPxiXXxftE</a> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zw47_q9wbBE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dzw47_q9wbBE&d=aS0Zid%2FrEVnhaHfkh5i1ak%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=d4bdf990\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zw47_q9wbBE</a><br />\n<br />\n評分: <br />\n平均分<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>98</strong></span> (@2017.3.6)<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.metacritic.com/game/switch/the-legend-of-zelda-breath-of-the-wild\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.metacritic.com%2Fgame%2Fswitch%2Fthe-legend-of-zelda-breath-of-the-wild&d=aS0Zid%2FrEVnhaHfkh5i1ak%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=ca150d30\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.metacritic.com/game/switch/the-legend-of-zelda-breath-of-the-wild</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://dystify.com/images/banner01.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdystify.com%2Fimages%2Fbanner01.png&h=041f6eef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nDLC:<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/HjuBG.md.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FHjuBG.md.jpg&h=9df1b11c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n舊post:<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/138930/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/138930/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/145768/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/145768/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"bccbc49be0c04bc8599accb92e13a4cbdf53fadc","tid":153282,"uid":72142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T13:02:23.000Z","msg":"想問下我依家係沙漠，身上有一set沙漠裝抗熱，同埋一件衫抗寒，咁依家我可以揀整一件頭用既防具，可以揀抗熱/寒，咁應該揀咩好？"},{"pid":"9db4b9d227ab036556b7af1bc8f5477bed37b2b5","tid":153282,"uid":72771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T14:12:25.000Z","msg":"石家象個大佬好難打，死咗成十幾次，究竟點樣過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa870e2a035051e512c59291061505c3872c3ef1","tid":153282,"uid":7593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T16:58:43.0