.000Z","msg":"求救收20枝電箭係咩玩法"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T02:42:18.000Z","msg":"好易架咋<br />\n跟指示上山頂有得執<br />\n唔好驚動隻人馬<br />\n有忍者衫就著<br />\n冇就當潛入game咁靜靜雞唔好俾佢聽/望到你<br />\n記得幫隻人馬影左相先<br />\n有個任要幫條女影隻人馬相<br />\n預先影唔洗去多次<br />\n獎品係卓拉裝條褲你可以上youtube搵埋教學<br />\n卓拉裝唔只件衫有全套架"},{"pid":"b6daf4babbe4437d491e2d7e7da3cc2e6cc40123","tid":153282,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T12:26:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb5c34993827eb1d777c3f1adbc8166aae4d30da","tid":153282,"uid":165336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b6daf4babbe4437d491e2d7e7da3cc2e6cc40123","tid":153282,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T12:26:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T14:34:11.000Z","msg":"我第一次入雪山見扣血已經去左睇攻略攞防寒衣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1f383f41913f69f7a25a6bcc6917f417db433ac","tid":153282,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb5c34993827eb1d777c3f1adbc8166aae4d30da","tid":153282,"uid":165336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b6daf4babbe4437d491e2d7e7da3cc2e6cc40123","tid":153282,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T12:26:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T14:34:11.000Z","msg":"我第一次入雪山見扣血已經去左睇攻略攞防寒衣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T14:41:29.000Z","msg":"見話點玩都得<br />\n所以隨心唔睇攻略玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}